Explanation of Lead Statuses & How Users Use Them

I’ve added customizable statuses to help users track leads through different sales stages. Here’s what each new status does and how users can use them:

1. Negotiation

Purpose:

  • This status is for leads that are actively discussing pricing, contracts, or terms before making a final decision.

How to Use:

  • When a lead expresses serious interest but needs more details, move them to "Negotiation."
  • Use this status to track leads that require discount offers, contract reviews, or competitor comparisons.
  • Add notes about what was discussed and schedule a follow-up call or meeting to finalize the deal.

✅ Example:

  • A company is interested in buying 500 test kits, but they need a bulk discount. Move them to Negotiation while you prepare a custom quote.

2. Closed Won

Purpose:

  • This status is for leads that have successfully converted into customers and completed a purchase.

How to Use:

  • When a lead makes a payment or places an order, change their status to "Closed Won."
  • Keep a record of order details and follow up with post-sale engagement (e.g., send an email thanking them and offering reorders).
  • Track the total number of "Closed Won" leads to measure sales success.

✅ Example:

  • A rehab center purchases 1,000 drug test cups after a negotiation. Update their status to Closed Won and send them a follow-up email.

3. Closed Lost

Purpose:

  • This status is for leads that decided not to purchase or are no longer interested.

How to Use:

  • When a lead explicitly declines the offer or chooses another vendor, change their status to "Closed Lost."
  • Use this status to track why leads were lost (price, competitors, timing issues, etc.).
  • Set a reminder to check back in a few months in case their situation changes.

✅ Example:

  • A staffing agency decides to go with a competitor's test kits. Move them to Closed Lost but schedule a follow-up in 6 months to check if they reconsider.

import { useState, useEffect } from "react";

export default function CRMApp() {
  const [leads, setLeads] = useState([]);
  const [newLead, setNewLead] = useState({ name: "", contact: "", phone: "", email: "", followUpDate: "", notes: "" });

  useEffect(() => {
    const today = new Date().toISOString().split("T")[0];
    leads.forEach(lead => {
      if (lead.followUpDate === today) {
        alert(`Reminder: Follow up with ${lead.name} today!`);
      }
    });
  }, [leads]);

  const addLead = () => {
    setLeads([...leads, { ...newLead, id: Date.now(), status: "New" }]);
    setNewLead({ name: "", contact: "", phone: "", email: "", followUpDate: "", notes: "" });
  };

  const updateLeadStatus = (id, status) => {
    setLeads(leads.map(lead => (lead.id === id ? { ...lead, status } : lead)));
  };

  return (
    <div style={{ padding: "20px", backgroundColor: "#F5F5F5", minHeight: "100vh" }}>
      <h1 style={{ fontSize: "24px", fontWeight: "bold", marginBottom: "20px", color: "#0073E6" }}>Simple CRM</h1>
      <div style={{ padding: "20px", border: "1px solid #0073E6", borderRadius: "8px", backgroundColor: "white" }}>
        <h2 style={{ fontSize: "20px", color: "#0073E6" }}>Add New Lead</h2>
        <div style={{ display: "grid", gridTemplateColumns: "1fr 1fr", gap: "10px", marginTop: "10px" }}>
          <input placeholder="Business Name" value={newLead.name} onChange={(e) => setNewLead({ ...newLead, name: e.target.value })} />
          <input placeholder="Contact Person" value={newLead.contact} onChange={(e) => setNewLead({ ...newLead, contact: e.target.value })} />
          <input placeholder="Phone Number" value={newLead.phone} onChange={(e) => setNewLead({ ...newLead, phone: e.target.value })} />
          <input placeholder="Email" value={newLead.email} onChange={(e) => setNewLead({ ...newLead, email: e.target.value })} />
          <input type="date" placeholder="Follow-Up Date" value={newLead.followUpDate} onChange={(e) => setNewLead({ ...newLead, followUpDate: e.target.value })} />
        </div>
        <button onClick={addLead} style={{ marginTop: "10px", padding: "10px", backgroundColor: "#0073E6", color: "white", border: "none", borderRadius: "4px" }}>
          Add Lead
        </button>
      </div>

      <table style={{ width: "100%", borderCollapse: "collapse", marginTop: "20px", border: "1px solid #0073E6" }}>
        <thead>
          <tr style={{ backgroundColor: "#FFD700", textAlign: "left" }}>
            <th style={{ padding: "10px" }}>Business</th>
            <th style={{ padding: "10px" }}>Contact</th>
            <th style={{ padding: "10px" }}>Phone</th>
            <th style={{ padding: "10px" }}>Email</th>
            <th style={{ padding: "10px" }}>Status</th>
            <th style={{ padding: "10px" }}>Follow-Up Date</th>
            <th style={{ padding: "10px" }}>Actions</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          {leads.map((lead) => (
            <tr key={lead.id} style={{ borderBottom: "1px solid #0073E6", textAlign: "left" }}>
              <td style={{ padding: "10px" }}>{lead.name}</td>
              <td style={{ padding: "10px" }}>{lead.contact}</td>
              <td style={{ padding: "10px" }}>{lead.phone}</td>
              <td style={{ padding: "10px" }}>{lead.email}</td>
              <td style={{ padding: "10px", fontWeight: "bold", color: "#0073E6" }}>{lead.status}</td>
              <td style={{ padding: "10px" }}>{lead.followUpDate}</td>
              <td style={{ padding: "10px", display: "flex", gap: "5px" }}>
                <button onClick={() => updateLeadStatus(lead.id, "Follow-up")} style={{ padding: "5px", backgroundColor: "#FFD700", color: "white", border: "none", borderRadius: "4px" }}>Follow-up</button>
                <button onClick={() => updateLeadStatus(lead.id, "Ready")} style={{ padding: "5px", backgroundColor: "#00A859", color: "white", border: "none", borderRadius: "4px" }}>Ready</button>
                <button onClick={() => updateLeadStatus(lead.id, "Negotiation")} style={{ padding: "5px", backgroundColor: "#FF8C00", color: "white", border: "none", borderRadius: "4px" }}>Negotiation</button>
                <button onClick={() => updateLeadStatus(lead.id, "Closed Won")} style={{ padding: "5px", backgroundColor: "#0073E6", color: "white", border: "none", borderRadius: "4px" }}>Closed Won</button>
                <button onClick={() => updateLeadStatus(lead.id, "Closed Lost")} style={{ padding: "5px", backgroundColor: "#FF3B30", color: "white", border: "none", borderRadius: "4px" }}>Closed Lost</button>
              </td>
            </tr>
          ))}
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

import { useState, useEffect } from "react";

const Card = ({ children }) => <div className="p-4 border rounded-lg shadow bg-white text-black w-full">{children}</div>;
const Button = ({ children, onClick, className }) => <button className={`p-2 text-white rounded ${className}`} onClick={onClick}>{children}</button>;
const Input = ({ type = "text", ...props }) => <input className="p-2 border rounded w-full bg-white text-black" type={type} {...props} />;
const Table = ({ children }) => <table className="w-full border-collapse border text-white">{children}</table>;

export default function CRMApp() {
const [leads, setLeads] = useState([]);
const [newLead, setNewLead] = useState({ name: "", contact: "", phone: "", email: "", followUpDate: "", dateCalled: "", notes: "", activityLog: [], score: 0 });

useEffect(() => {
const today = new Date().toISOString().split("T")[0];
leads.forEach(lead => {
if (lead.followUpDate === today) {
alert(`Reminder: Follow up with ${lead.name} today!`);
}
});
}, [leads]);

const addLead = () => {
setLeads([...leads, { ...newLead, id: Date.now(), status: "New", dateCalled: new Date().toLocaleDateString(), activityLog: [], score: 0 }]);
setNewLead({ name: "", contact: "", phone: "", email: "", followUpDate: "", notes: "", dateCalled: "", activityLog: [], score: 0 });
};

return (
<div className="p-4 bg-[#A0A3A8] min-h-screen text-white w-full flex flex-col items-center">
<img src='/mnt/data/Create_a_premium_and_high-value_logo_for_CloseWise.png' alt='CloseWise CRM Logo' className='mb-4 w-64 h-auto' />
<Card className="w-full max-w-6xl border border-[#0073E6]">
<h2 className="text-lg font-semibold text-[#0073E6]">Add New Lead</h2>
<div className="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-2">
<Input placeholder="Business Name" value={newLead.name} onChange={(e) => setNewLead({ ...newLead, name: e.target.value })} />
<Input placeholder="Contact Person" value={newLead.contact} onChange={(e) => setNewLead({ ...newLead, contact: e.target.value })} />
<Input placeholder="Phone Number" value={newLead.phone} onChange={(e) => setNewLead({ ...newLead, phone: e.target.value })} />
<Input placeholder="Email" value={newLead.email} onChange={(e) => setNewLead({ ...newLead, email: e.target.value })} />
</div>
<Button className="mt-2 bg-[#0073E6] px-8 py-4 text-lg text-white text-left w-auto" onClick={addLead}>Add Lead</Button>
</Card>
<Table className="w-full max-w-6xl mt-4 border border-[#0073E6]">
<thead>
<tr className="bg-[#FFD700] text-left text-black">
<th className="p-2 text-left">Business</th>
<th className="p-2 text-left">Contact</th>
<th className="p-2 text-left">Phone</th>
<th className="p-2 text-left">Email</th>
<th className="p-2 text-left">Status</th>
<th className="p-2 text-left">Follow-Up Date</th>
<th className="p-2 text-left">Activity Log</th>
<th className="p-2 text-left">Score</th>
<th className="p-2 text-left">Date Called</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
{leads.map((lead) => (
<tr key={lead.id} className="border-b border-[#0073E6] text-left">
<td className="p-2"><Input type="text" value={lead.name} onChange={(e) => setLeads(leads.map(l => l.id === lead.id ? { ...l, name: e.target.value } : l))} /></td>
<td className="p-2"><Input type="text" value={lead.contact} onChange={(e) => setLeads(leads.map(l => l.id === lead.id ? { ...l, contact: e.target.value } : l))} /></td>
<td className="p-2"><Input type="text" value={lead.phone} onChange={(e) => setLeads(leads.map(l => l.id === lead.id ? { ...l, phone: e.target.value } : l))} /></td>
<td className="p-2"><Input type="text" value={lead.email} onChange={(e) => setLeads(leads.map(l => l.id === lead.id ? { ...l, email: e.target.value } : l))} /></td>
<td className="p-2">
<select className="p-2 border rounded w-full bg-white text-black" value={lead.status} onChange={(e) => setLeads(leads.map(l => l.id === lead.id ? { ...l, status: e.target.value } : l))}>
<option value="New">New</option>
<option value="Follow-up">Follow-up</option>
<option value="Ready">Ready</option>
<option value="Negotiation">Negotiation</option>
<option value="Closed Won">Closed Won</option>
<option value="Closed Lost">Closed Lost</option>
</select>
</td>
<td className="p-2"><Input type="date" value={lead.followUpDate} onChange={(e) => setLeads(leads.map(l => l.id === lead.id ? { ...l, followUpDate: e.target.value } : l))} /></td>
<td className="p-2"><textarea className="p-2 border rounded w-full bg-white text-black" value={lead.activityLog ? lead.activityLog.join('\n') : ''} onChange={(e) => setLeads(leads.map(l => l.id === lead.id ? { ...l, activityLog: e.target.value.split('\n') } : l))}></textarea></td>
<td className="p-2"><input type="number" className="p-2 border rounded w-full bg-white text-black" value={lead.score || 0} onChange={(e) => setLeads(leads.map(l => l.id === lead.id ? { ...l, score: Number(e.target.value) } : l))} /></td>
<td className="p-2"><input type="text" className="p-2 border rounded w-full bg-white text-black" value={lead.dateCalled} disabled /></td>
</tr>
))}
</tbody>
</Table>
</div>
);
}
